name: guozi_anime
description:
擅长画动漫风格，与lora融合效果好，对中式风格把握的还不错。点一点喜欢，后续会更新一些好用的模型和lora。欢迎返图，提示词注意加上Chinese color_ink painting style，会有不错的中式风格。

Good at drawing animation style, good integration effect with lora, and good grasp of Chinese style. Like it a little bit, and some useful models and lora will be updated later. Welcome back to the picture, please add Chinese color_ink painting style to the prompt word, it will have a good Chinese style.
